ly eccentric kinematic disk component, which may have been\ncaused by a disruptive event thought to have taken place at a closer-in\nlocation in the disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 19:11:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-24"}
